{"tid":1050832,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣係excel 用按鍵選打橫一行","createTime":"2019-03-07T06:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T11:30:17.000Z","uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb888d2c49b4c104904ff8ec561d6c13a1f5fa3","tid":1050832,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"我知道係用 shift + space <br />\n<br />\n但係用中文輸入既時候 shift + space 又俾佢霸左轉 全/半形 <br />\n<br />\n我亦都知道理論上可以去語言選擇可以揀停左全/半 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zr9V6O7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzr9V6O7.jpg&h=450b6bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過咁啱 MS 原來又有個 bug， 就係呢個全/半無論你點改都係會去翻 shift + space <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 無得停。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.henrypoon.com/blog/2012/01/03/removing-the-annoying-windows-language-hotkeys-ctrlspace-shiftspace-etc-that-toggles-the-full-widthhalf-width-characters-on-the-chinese-ime/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.henrypoon.com%2Fblog%2F2012%2F01%2F03%2Fremoving-the-annoying-windows-language-hotkeys-ctrlspace-shiftspace-etc-that-toggles-the-full-widthhalf-width-characters-on-the-chinese-ime%2F%20&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=966b5ce0\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.henrypoon.com/blog/2012/01/03/removing-the-annoying-windows-language-hotkeys-ctrlspace-shiftspace-etc-that-toggles-the-full-widthhalf-width-characters-on-the-chinese-ime/ </a><br />\n<br />\nexcel 又無得揀用第二個keyboard shortcut。甚至連上面D drop down menu都無呢樣野， 唯一既方法就係用mouse 襟。 <br />\n<br />\n有無人有其他方法？ 我連 autohotkey 都用埋諗唔到解決方法。"},{"pid":"1c36272fd4b2d9a1509a6d2771c5d85f1b6c3907","tid":1050832,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"轉返去美式鍵盤先咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbc3e9a46e71d651575f8e82aa9ae97894a8944","tid":1050832,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":